here's your meds.

21
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:13,080
Remember to take it on time.

22
00:02:26,290 --> 00:02:26,910
Here,

23
00:02:27,040 --> 00:02:28,000
have some tea.

24
00:02:28,160 --> 00:02:29,750
It's a fresh batch,

25
00:02:29,910 --> 00:02:31,160
and I brewed it myself.

26
00:02:41,700 --> 00:02:42,830
Chengchi.

27
00:02:47,370 --> 00:02:48,870
Mrs. Gu, I see what you're doing.

28
00:02:49,330 --> 00:02:51,370
You're pulling out all the stops

29
00:02:51,700 --> 00:02:54,080
to split up me and En.

30
00:02:58,500 --> 00:03:00,410
Well, we'll see if it works.

31
00:03:00,660 --> 00:03:01,500
Let's go.

32
00:03:44,640 --> 00:03:47,270
[Shishi City Hospital]

33
00:03:57,700 --> 00:03:58,830
Chu,

34
00:04:00,540 --> 00:04:02,620
how long are you going to sleep?

35
00:04:03,330 --> 00:04:05,700
It's been 15 days.

36
00:04:05,700 --> 00:04:07,930
♪Still can't be sure♪

37
00:04:09,700 --> 00:04:10,790
Do you know

38
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:13,250
your magazine is releasing a new issue?

39
00:04:13,660 --> 00:04:15,080
Without you in charge,

40
00:04:15,160 --> 00:04:16,700
the quality's dropped.

41
00:04:17,080 --> 00:04:18,620
And your team

42
00:04:18,750 --> 00:04:19,790
is burning out,

43
00:04:19,870 --> 00:04:21,950
pulling all-nighters,

44
00:04:22,080 --> 00:04:23,870
and complaining.

45
00:04:24,750 --> 00:04:27,330
You've become the backbone

46
00:04:28,370 --> 00:04:29,450
of the company

47
00:04:29,500 --> 00:04:31,700
in just a few years.

48
00:04:32,500 --> 00:04:33,750
Come on,

49
00:04:34,700 --> 00:04:36,500
they need you.

50
00:04:37,200 --> 00:04:38,830
You need to wake up.

51
00:04:38,950 --> 00:04:41,750
It's falling apart without you.

52
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:44,160
You wouldn't want that, right?

53
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,200
And I...

54
00:04:50,580 --> 00:04:53,200
I've been thinking a lot lately,

55
00:04:54,290 --> 00:04:54,870
trying to figure out

56
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:57,080
what I've done to you.

57
00:04:57,870 --> 00:05:00,620
I tried to remember times
when I treated you well,

58
00:05:02,120 --> 00:05:04,120
but all I see are mistakes,

59
00:05:05,200 --> 00:05:07,500
pulling you away from the Gu family,

60
00:05:07,830 --> 00:05:10,040
pushing you to forget Han Chengchi,

61
00:05:10,500 --> 00:05:11,750
and even...

62
00:05:12,330 --> 00:05:14,250
trying to prove I care

63
00:05:14,370 --> 00:05:15,870
by making you upset.

64
00:05:17,200 --> 00:05:19,540
None of them was nice.

65
00:05:21,700 --> 00:05:24,660
I never considered your feelings.

66
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:46,220
♪You're always away♪

67
00:05:46,700 --> 00:05:48,120
It's all my fault.

68
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:49,370
♪Our bond won't stay♪

69
00:05:49,370 --> 00:05:51,620
My selfish love

70
00:05:52,910 --> 00:05:55,540
has caused you so much pain.

71
00:05:55,540 --> 00:05:57,540
♪Hurt me all the way♪

72
00:05:58,910 --> 00:05:59,950
Chu,

73
00:06:04,790 --> 00:06:06,910
maybe it's time for me to let go.

74
00:06:06,910 --> 00:06:10,220
♪Our problem was clear♪

75
00:06:10,560 --> 00:06:14,350
♪I lost myself here♪

76
00:06:15,790 --> 00:06:16,830
Alright.

77
00:06:19,700 --> 00:06:21,120
I promise you,

78
00:06:23,540 --> 00:06:24,870
if you wake up,

79
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:27,910
as soon as you wake up,

80
00:06:31,250 --> 00:06:33,040
I'll let go.

81
00:06:35,330 --> 00:06:36,660
I'll agree to the divorce,

82
00:06:38,950 --> 00:06:40,080
okay?

83
00:06:40,080 --> 00:06:42,640
♪A smile is the classy thing♪

84
00:06:42,640 --> 00:06:48,930
♪I've bet everything♪

85
00:06:50,930 --> 00:06:54,810
♪I think of her, no reply♪

86
00:06:54,810 --> 00:06:58,850
♪Scars don't heal, still I try♪

87
00:06:58,850 --> 00:07:02,140
♪I said I wouldn't cry♪

88
00:07:02,140 --> 00:07:06,060
♪Even at the brink♪

89
00:07:07,370 --> 00:07:08,500
Chu.

90
00:07:10,250 --> 00:07:11,620
Chu, you're awake?

91
00:07:11,620 --> 00:07:14,600
♪My voice hoarse, tears in sync♪

92
00:07:14,620 --> 00:07:15,540
Chu.

93
00:07:15,700 --> 00:07:16,370
Chu.

94
00:07:16,540 --> 00:07:17,500
Doctor!

95
00:07:18,250 --> 00:07:19,290
Doctor!

96
00:07:19,290 --> 00:07:26,220
♪I've bet everything♪

97
00:07:38,060 --> 00:07:39,970
[Jiayi: En, are you ready?]

98
00:07:45,910 --> 00:07:48,540
Lanshan, I knew you'd be fine.

99
00:07:48,750 --> 00:07:50,500
You can do it. I believe in you.

100
00:07:51,500 --> 00:07:53,410
I'm fine. Don't worry.

101
00:07:54,540 --> 00:07:55,330
By the way,

102
00:07:55,790 --> 00:07:57,200
Chengchi,

103
00:07:57,700 --> 00:07:58,830
how is he?

104
00:07:59,080 --> 00:07:59,910
Chengchi?

105
00:08:00,200 --> 00:08:01,120
He's alright.

106
00:08:01,250 --> 00:08:02,580
He was discharged today.

107
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:04,950
What about

108
00:08:05,120 --> 00:08:06,200
my sister?

109
00:08:06,500 --> 00:08:07,700
She's good.

110
00:08:07,830 --> 00:08:09,910
She's marrying Lu Yifan next month.

111
00:08:10,080 --> 00:08:11,040
What?

112
00:08:11,790 --> 00:08:12,790
Lu Yifan?

113
00:08:13,910 --> 00:08:15,870
After 20 years together,

114
00:08:15,950 --> 00:08:17,120
they just broke up like that.

115
00:08:17,700 --> 00:08:19,120
That's wild.

116
00:08:39,790 --> 00:08:41,080
Liunian just called.

117
00:08:41,790 --> 00:08:43,160
Lanshan's awake.

118
00:08:44,330 --> 00:08:45,700
And he

119
00:08:46,250 --> 00:08:47,660
passed on your message.

120
00:08:56,830 --> 00:08:57,750
Shwenny,

121
00:08:59,540 --> 00:09:01,450
you can't keep avoiding this.

122
00:09:03,290 --> 00:09:04,870
You stayed by her side every day

123
00:09:05,330 --> 00:09:07,370
while she was out.

124
00:09:08,410 --> 00:09:09,790
Now that she's awake,

125
00:09:10,500 --> 00:09:11,950
you should go see her.

126
00:09:13,750 --> 00:09:15,540
I finally understand

127
00:09:15,620 --> 00:09:16,950
what you meant before.

128
00:09:17,410 --> 00:09:18,540
Porcupines

129
00:09:18,700 --> 00:09:20,540
never lower their quills...

130
00:09:21,080 --> 00:09:22,080
Do you know

131
00:09:22,750 --> 00:09:25,080
when porcupines lower their quills?

132
00:09:25,890 --> 00:09:27,700
♪Softly saying goodbye, set free♪

133
00:09:27,700 --> 00:09:28,870
unless

134
00:09:30,290 --> 00:09:31,580
they're dead.

135
00:09:32,660 --> 00:09:33,660
Shwenny...

136
00:09:33,660 --> 00:09:36,970
♪Reliving sweet times with you♪

137
00:09:37,270 --> 00:09:44,060
♪But in your world, I was blank♪

138
00:09:44,060 --> 00:09:47,850
♪I don't want to give up yet♪

139
00:09:48,410 --> 00:09:49,790
I promise you,

140
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:53,620
if you wake up,

141
00:09:53,830 --> 00:09:55,870
I'll let go.

142
00:09:57,910 --> 00:09:59,450
I'll agree to the divorce.

143
00:09:59,450 --> 00:10:03,310
♪Through the crowd, I hug you tight♪

144
00:10:03,310 --> 00:10:07,680
♪Like raindrops in the cool night♪

145
00:10:08,020 --> 00:10:12,470
♪Memories frozen, love so bright♪

146
00:10:12,470 --> 00:10:18,770
♪I don't want to forget.
I don't want to give up yet♪

147
00:10:18,770 --> 00:10:22,720
♪Give me a breath, just one more chance♪

148
00:10:22,720 --> 00:10:25,930
♪But your trail I can't detect♪

149
00:10:25,930 --> 00:10:30,520
♪You've gone, no trace left♪

150
00:10:31,640 --> 00:10:35,770
[Divorce Agreement]

151
00:10:36,160 --> 00:10:37,450
If we don't see you,

152
00:10:38,910 --> 00:10:41,000
can we stay married?

153
00:10:43,350 --> 00:10:50,390
♪I don't want to forget our light♪

154
00:11:13,870 --> 00:11:15,870
Alright, call me if you need anything.

155
00:11:20,830 --> 00:11:21,790
En.

156
00:11:27,910 --> 00:11:29,330
Can't believe you actually showed up.

157
00:11:29,540 --> 00:11:30,450
En,

158
00:11:30,700 --> 00:11:31,620
please believe me.

159
00:11:31,700 --> 00:11:33,950
Nothing happened
between Chengchi and me.

160
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:35,370
Believe you?

161
00:11:36,790 --> 00:11:39,120
Believe you never had feelings for him?

162
00:11:40,250 --> 00:11:41,540
Or that you didn't kiss him

163
00:11:41,620 --> 00:11:42,950
in front of everyone?

164
00:11:43,910 --> 00:11:44,870
En,

165
00:11:45,500 --> 00:11:47,660
it's my fault.

166
00:11:48,250 --> 00:11:50,750
But please don't

167
00:11:50,910 --> 00:11:53,750
marry someone you don't love.

168
00:11:53,910 --> 00:11:56,120
It'll ruin your life.

169
00:11:59,790 --> 00:12:00,790
Gu Lanshan,

170
00:12:01,250 --> 00:12:02,290
you are the last person

171
00:12:02,410 --> 00:12:04,200
who should be giving me advice.

172
00:12:04,500 --> 00:12:05,830
If I end up unhappy,

173
00:12:06,160 --> 00:12:07,870
it's all on you!

174
00:12:09,290 --> 00:12:10,290
En,

175
00:12:10,750 --> 00:12:12,040
please give Chengchi another chance.

176
00:12:12,160 --> 00:12:14,250
He truly loves you.

177
00:12:26,160 --> 00:12:27,330
Truly?

178
00:12:28,370 --> 00:12:29,660
I can't even trust

179
00:12:29,750 --> 00:12:31,540
my own sister.

180
00:12:32,250 --> 00:12:34,040
Who am I supposed to trust?

181
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:37,250
From now on,

182
00:12:38,040 --> 00:12:39,790
you're not my sister!

183
00:12:41,830 --> 00:12:42,750
Lanshan,

184
00:12:43,750 --> 00:12:45,410
people are selfish.

185
00:12:46,080 --> 00:12:47,160
I'm sorry.

186
00:13:21,500 --> 00:13:22,370
Excuse me.

187
00:13:22,580 --> 00:13:23,580
I want to know

188
00:13:23,750 --> 00:13:24,750
why my light was left on

189
00:13:24,870 --> 00:13:26,200
when I wasn't there.

190
00:13:26,830 --> 00:13:28,040
Your husband asked us to.

191
00:13:28,250 --> 00:13:28,950
He said you're afraid of the dark

192
00:13:29,040 --> 00:13:30,160
and wanted the light left on for you.

193
00:13:30,620 --> 00:13:31,200
Look,

194
00:13:31,290 --> 00:13:32,870
he even left a list of instructions.

195
00:13:34,620 --> 00:13:36,040
Your husband really cares about you.

196
00:13:36,290 --> 00:13:38,290
He not only left these notes

197
00:13:38,500 --> 00:13:40,290
but also comes by
around 1 a.m. every day

198
00:13:40,410 --> 00:13:41,580
to spend time with you.

199
00:13:41,910 --> 00:13:42,910
All of us nurses

200
00:13:43,000 --> 00:13:44,250
are jealous.

201
00:13:50,870 --> 00:13:51,870
Thank you.

202
00:13:51,950 --> 00:13:53,200
Get some rest.

203
00:14:00,810 --> 00:14:03,720
♪Rainy days, emotions dance♪

204
00:14:04,560 --> 00:14:07,810
♪Hard to shake the words of pain♪

205
00:14:08,430 --> 00:14:13,310
♪Took so long, but still remains♪

206
00:14:15,720 --> 00:14:18,560
♪Passing by that old street sign♪

207
00:14:19,470 --> 00:14:22,140
♪Feels like you might still be mine♪

208
00:14:24,890 --> 00:14:26,430
[Sheng Shi]

209
00:14:31,770 --> 00:14:33,810
[Typing...]

210
00:14:33,810 --> 00:14:37,100
♪Both of us with debts unpaid♪

211
00:14:39,850 --> 00:14:41,220
[To Sheng Shi: Where are you?]

212
00:14:43,930 --> 00:14:46,430
[To Sheng Shi: I've been doing well.
How about you?]

213
00:14:49,020 --> 00:14:51,180
♪Wishing our story replayed♪

214
00:14:51,180 --> 00:14:52,680
[Sheng Shi]

215
00:14:52,680 --> 00:14:54,970
♪Love doesn't always find its way♪

216
00:14:54,970 --> 00:14:58,810
♪Starts don't mean we'll stay♪

217
00:14:58,810 --> 00:15:00,680
♪When they leave, we cope♪

218
00:15:00,680 --> 00:15:02,770
♪Strangers judge, we hope♪

219
00:15:02,770 --> 00:15:04,680
♪Stories told again♪

220
00:15:04,680 --> 00:15:06,930
♪Who felt pain back then♪

221
00:15:07,060 --> 00:15:10,220
♪We never learned restraint♪

222
00:15:10,220 --> 00:15:13,810
♪No need to hide our pain♪

223
00:15:13,810 --> 00:15:17,520
♪Memories blur, truth fades♪

224
00:15:17,520 --> 00:15:21,680
♪Feelings spread as trends invade♪

225
00:15:21,680 --> 00:15:24,890
♪So we part, hearts in doubt♪

226
00:15:24,890 --> 00:15:28,390
♪Tonight, no sleep throughout♪

227
00:15:45,620 --> 00:15:46,370
Ms. Gu,

228
00:15:46,540 --> 00:15:47,540
Mr. Han has been waiting outside

229
00:15:47,660 --> 00:15:49,000
for you all night.

230
00:15:51,390 --> 00:15:52,270
[Delete one photo]

231
00:15:52,600 --> 00:15:53,970
[Delete]

232
00:16:12,290 --> 00:16:13,290
After everything you did,

233
00:16:13,370 --> 00:16:14,580
you still have the nerve to show up?

234
00:16:15,500 --> 00:16:16,500
Just go.

235
00:16:18,750 --> 00:16:19,790
I'm not leaving

236
00:16:20,120 --> 00:16:21,160
until I see En.

237
00:16:21,790 --> 00:16:22,910
You know

238
00:16:23,330 --> 00:16:24,500
what happened

239
00:16:24,700 --> 00:16:26,290
isn't what she thinks.

240
00:16:26,500 --> 00:16:28,700
What good does that do now?

241
00:16:29,330 --> 00:16:31,830
En is about to marry Lu Yifan.

242
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:35,580
We're already engaged.

243
00:16:35,830 --> 00:16:37,450
Why can't you just let it go?

244
00:16:37,950 --> 00:16:39,250
So what if you're engaged?

245
00:16:39,910 --> 00:16:41,500
I'm not letting En live a life

246
00:16:41,620 --> 00:16:43,080
with no future.

247
00:16:43,370 --> 00:16:44,370
Don't waste your time

248
00:16:44,500 --> 00:16:45,700
trying to explain.

249
00:16:45,830 --> 00:16:47,080
She won't believe you.

250
00:16:47,290 --> 00:16:48,660
If you're smart,

251
00:16:49,080 --> 00:16:51,160
you'll stay out of her life.

252
00:16:54,500 --> 00:16:55,370
Mrs. Gu.

253
00:16:55,620 --> 00:16:57,000
Yifan, you're here.

254
00:16:57,870 --> 00:16:59,250
And look who it is.

255
00:17:03,000 --> 00:17:05,040
Do you really think you belong here?

256
00:17:06,870 --> 00:17:08,120
Oh, I'm so scared.

257
00:17:08,500 --> 00:17:08,870
Are you going to

258
00:17:08,910 --> 00:17:10,700
talk with your fists?

259
00:17:16,120 --> 00:17:18,120
You done? Fine, I'm going in.

260
00:17:21,700 --> 00:17:22,660
Mrs. Gu.

261
00:17:22,750 --> 00:17:23,700
En is waiting upstairs.

262
00:17:23,700 --> 00:17:24,700
- Go on.
- Okay.

263
00:17:33,290 --> 00:17:34,290
Chengchi,

264
00:17:34,660 --> 00:17:36,000
don't blame me.

265
00:17:36,410 --> 00:17:38,870
I just want the best for En.

266
00:17:39,330 --> 00:17:40,370
You and her

267
00:17:40,620 --> 00:17:41,790
weren't meant to be.

268
00:18:02,540 --> 00:18:03,250
Chengchi,

269
00:18:03,370 --> 00:18:04,660
come on, let's go home.

270
00:18:04,870 --> 00:18:06,160
I haven't seen En yet.

271
00:18:06,410 --> 00:18:07,200
You should go.

272
00:18:07,290 --> 00:18:08,910
What do you think you're doing?

273
00:18:09,120 --> 00:18:10,500
Are you stupid?

274
00:18:10,660 --> 00:18:12,250
You really don't get it?

275
00:18:12,750 --> 00:18:14,660
It's not just about what happened.

276
00:18:14,790 --> 00:18:16,870
She's leaving because of the bankruptcy.

277
00:18:16,950 --> 00:18:17,910
That's not true.

278
00:18:18,540 --> 00:18:19,830
En still loves me.

279
00:18:20,750 --> 00:18:21,790
Just go.

280
00:18:22,290 --> 00:18:23,500
You don't understand.

281
00:18:45,160 --> 00:18:46,080
What's up?

282
00:18:49,000 --> 00:18:49,950
What?

283
00:18:53,830 --> 00:18:54,790
Get everyone

284
00:18:54,870 --> 00:18:56,620
to the office.

285
00:18:56,790 --> 00:18:58,000
I'm heading back now.

286
00:20:08,660 --> 00:20:10,910
[Sheng Scandal! Love Affair Turns Sour]
What's going on?

287
00:20:11,250 --> 00:20:13,500
This story broke overnight,

288
00:20:13,750 --> 00:20:16,330
and it's already viral!

289
00:20:16,620 --> 00:20:18,540
It's been shared
